import {
  Button,
  Card,
  CardActions,
  CardContent,
  makeStyles,
  TextField,
  Typography,
} from "@material-ui/core"

const useStyles = makeStyles((theme) => ({
  feed: {
    maxWidth: "256",
  },
}))

const Feed = (props) => {
  return (
    <Card>
      <CardContent>
        <Typography component="h2" variant="h5">
          {props.post}
        </Typography>
      </CardContent>
      <CardActions>
        <Button size="small">Comments ({props.comments})</Button>
        <Button size="small">Likes ({props.likes})</Button>
      </CardActions>
      <CardActions>
        <TextField
          fullWidth
          label="Add a comment"
          name="comment"
          size="small"
          variant="outlined"
        />
        <Button color="primary">Submit</Button>
      </CardActions>
    </Card>
  )
}

export default Feed
